












                                     CPAN::Mini to the rescue!
          
          * What is CPAN::Mini?
          
          * creates a minimal mirror of CPAN
          
          * only the files needed to install the newest version of every CPAN distribution: 
          
            * index files:
              *   01mailrc.txt.gz
              *   02packages.details.txt.gz
              *   03modlist.data.gz
          
























